Clinical and molecular predictors of mortality in neurofibromatosis 2: a UK 
national analysis of 1192 patients.

Hexter A(1), Jones A(2), Joe H(2), Heap L(1), Smith MJ(3), Wallace AJ(1), 
Halliday D(4), Parry A(5), Taylor A(6), Raymond L(6), Shaw A(7), Afridi S(8), 
Obholzer R(9), Axon P(10), King AT(11); English Specialist NF2 Research Group; 
