Pharmacogenetics as a tool to tailor antiretroviral therapy: A review.

Aceti A(1), Gianserra L(1), Lambiase L(1), Pennica A(1), Teti E(1).

Author information:
(1)Antonio Aceti, Laura Gianserra, Lara Lambiase, Alfredo Pennica, Elisabetta 
